date=February 16, 2017|accessdate=March 6, 2019}}</ref> At [[Anime Expo]] on July 5, 2018, J-Novel Club announced that the series would be published in print with [[Ingram Content Group|Ingram Publisher Services]].<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.animenewsnetwork.com/news/2018-07-05/j-novel-club-announces-print-publishing-line-with-in-another-world-with-my-smartphone-novels/.133845 |title=J-Novel Club Announces Print Publishing Line With In Another World with My Smartphone Novels |last=Ressler |first=Karen |date=July 5, 2018 |website=[[Anime News Network]] |accessdate=July 5, 2018 }}</ref> The novel series was adapted into a manga series by Soto began serialization in the January 2017 issue of [[Comp Ace]] (published November 2016),<ref>{{cite web|title=\u30b3\u30f3\u30d7\u30a8\u30fc\u30b9 2017\u5e741\u6708\u53f7|url=https://web-ace.jp/compace/backnumber/detail/65/|website=\u30b3\u30f3\u30d7\u30a8\u30fc\u30b9|publisher=Kadokawa Corporation|accessdate=January 24, 2018}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=\u30b3\u30f3\u30d7\u30a8\u30fc\u30b9 2017\u5e741\u6708\u53f7|url=https://www.amazon.co.jp/dp/B01N3OH390|website=Amazon Japan|accessdate=January 24, 2018}}</ref> with the first two compiled [[tank\u014dbon]] volumes released consecutively in June and July 2017 and the third volume in February 2018.<ref name=\"Manga Vol 1\" /><ref name=\"Manga Vol 2\" /><ref name=\"Manga Vol 3\" />\n__TOC__\n\n==Light novel==\n{{Graphic novel list/header\n| Language        = Japanese\n| SecondLanguage  = English\n}}\n{{Graphic novel list\n| VolumeNumber = 1\n| OriginalRelDate = May 22, 2015<ref>{{cite web|url=https://hobbyjapan.co.jp/hjnovels/lineup/detail/11.html|title=\u7570\u4e16\u754c\u306f\u30b9\u30de\u30fc\u30c8\u30d5\u30a9\u30f3\u3068\u3068\u3082\u306b\u3002\uff11|publisher=[[Hobby Japan]] |work=[[HJ Novels]] |language=Japanese |accessdate=July 11, 2017}}</ref>\n| OriginalISBN = 978-4-79-861018-4\n| LicensedRelDate = March 23, 2017 (E-book)<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.amazon.com/dp/B06XBJKYS7|title=In Another World with My Smartphone: Volume 1 (E-book)|publisher=[[Amazon (company)|amazon]]|accessdate=July 20, 2019}}</ref><br/>February 5, 2019 (print)<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.amazon.com/dp/1718350007|title=In Another World with My Smartphone: Volume 1 (print)|publisher=[[Amazon (company)|amazon]]|accessdate=July 20, 2019}}</ref>\n| ChapterListCol1 =\n* Prologue\n* Chapter I: {{Nihongo|\"In Another World\"|\u7570\u4e16\u754c\u306b\u7acb\u3064|Isekai ni Tatsu}}\n* Chapter II: {{Nihongo|\"The More The Merrier! Double the Joy, Half the Sorrow\"|\u65c5\u306f\u9053\u9023\u308c\u3001\u4e16\u306f\u60c5\u3051|Tabi wa Michizure, Yo wa Nasake}}\n* Chapter III: {{Nihongo|\"The Crystal Creature\"|\u6c34\u6676\u306e\u602a\u7269|Suish\u014d no Kaibutsu}}\n| ChapterListCol2 =\n* Chapter IV: {{Nihongo|\"The Royal Family\"|\u738b\u5bb6\u306e\u4eba\u3005|\u014cke no Hitobito}}\n* Interlude I: {{Nihongo|\"The Adventures\"|\u5192\u967a\u8005\u305f\u3061|B\u014dkensha-tachi}}\n* Interlude II: {{Nihongo|\"A Day in the Capital\"|\u738b\u90fd\u306e\u4e00\u65e5|\u014cto no Ichinichi}}\n| LicensedISBN    = 978-1-7183-5000-7\n| Summary = \n}}\n{{Graphic novel list\n| VolumeNumber = 2\n| OriginalRelDate = August 22, 2015<ref>{{cite web|url=https://hobbyjapan.co.jp/hjnovels/lineup/detail/15.html|title=\u7570\u4e16\u754c\u306f\u30b9\u30de\u30fc\u30c8\u30d5\u30a9\u30f3\u3068\u3068\u3082\u306b\u30022|publisher=[[Hobby Japan]] |work=HJ Novels|language=Japanese |accessdate=July 11, 2017}}</ref>\n| ISBN = 978-4-79-861065-8\n| LicensedRelDate = May 4, 2017 (E-book)<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.amazon.com/dp/B06Y14VGZT|title=In Another World with My Smartphone: Volume 2 (E-book)|publisher=[[Amazon (company)|amazon]]|accessdate=July 20, 2019}}</ref><br/>February 5, 2019 (print)<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.amazon.com/dp/1718350015|title=In Another World with My Smartphone: Volume 2 (print)|publisher=[[Amazon (company)|amazon]]|accessdate=July 20, 2019}}</ref>\n| LicensedISB