ei no Gi}}\n* Interlude: {{Nihongo|\"A Myriad of Love\"|\u604b\u5fc3\u8272\u3005|Koigokoro Iroiro}}\n| Summary = \n}}\n{{Graphic novel list\n| VolumeNumber = 8\n| OriginalRelDate = March 23, 2017<ref>{{cite web|url=https://hobbyjapan.co.jp/hjnovels/lineup/detail/73.html|title=\u7570\u4e16\u754c\u306f\u30b9\u30de\u30fc\u30c8\u30d5\u30a9\u30f3\u3068\u3068\u3082\u306b\u30028|publisher=[[Hobby Japan]] |work=HJ Novels|language=Japanese |accessdate=July 11, 2017}}</ref>\n| OriginalISBN = 978-4-79-861415-1 \n| LicensedRelDate = May 10, 2018 (E-book)<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.amazon.com/dp/B07BK54Q69|title=In Another World with My Smartphone: Volume 8 (E-book)|publisher=[[Amazon (company)|amazon]]|accessdate=July 20, 2019}}</ref><br/> February 4, 2020 (print)<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.amazon.com/dp/1718350074|title=In Another World with My Smartphone: Volume 8 (print)|publisher=[[Amazon (company)|amazon]]|accessdate=July 20, 2019}}</ref>\n| LicensedISBN    = 978-1-7183-5007-6\n| ChapterListCol1 =\n* Chapter I: {{Nihongo|\"The Archieves of Wisdom\"|\u53e1\u667a\u306e\u66f8\u5eab|Eichi no Shoko}}\n* Chapter II: {{Nihongo|\"Dungeons & Dragons\"|\u30c0\u30f3\u30b8\u30e7\u30f3\u30ba\uff06\u30c9\u30e9\u30b4\u30f3\u30ba|Danjonzu & Doragonzu}}\n* Chapter III: {{Nihongo|\"The Dungeon's Conspiracy\"|\u9670\u8b00\u306e\u8ff7\u5bae|Inb\u014d no Meik\u016b}}\n| ChapterListCol2 =\n* Interlude I: {{Nihongo|\"The Trial of the Fairies\"|\u5996\u7cbe\u306e\u8a66\u7df4|Y\u014dsei no Shiren}}\n* Interlude II: {{Nihongo|\"The Die Is Cast\"|\u8cfd\u306f\u6295\u3052\u3089\u308c\u305f|Sai wa Nagerareta}}\n| Summary = \n}}\n{{Graphic novel list\n| VolumeNumber = 9\n| OriginalRelDate = June 22, 2017<ref>{{cite web|url=https://hobbyjapan.co.jp/hjnovels/lineup/detail/86.html|title=\u7570\u4e16\u754c\u306f\u30b9\u30de\u30fc\u30c8\u30d5\u30a9\u30f3\u3068\u3068\u3082\u306b\u30029|publisher=[[Hobby Japan]] |work=HJ Novels|language=Japanese |accessdate=August 7, 2017}}</ref>\n| OriginalISBN = 978